-- Cofidis Rider Arrested on Tour de France, AFP News Agency Says
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-07-10T11:20:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-10/cofidis-rider-arrested-on-tour-de-france-afp-news-agency-says.html
A French rider from the Cofidis team
on cycling’s  Tour de France  has been arrested in connection with
alleged doping, Agence France-Presse reported.  Two other unidentified men have been taken into custody in
Marseille, the news agency added.  Earlier, police raided the Cofidis team’s hotel at
Bourg-en-Bresse during the Tour’s first rest day, AFP said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  